{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::d5cc24ea-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nEmbark on an unforgettable charter experience aboard the Lagoon 46 “Kalisi Mou.” This exquisite catamaran combines luxury, comfort, and style to create an enchanting sailing adventure. With an obligatory skipper to navigate the waters and the option to have a hostess attend to your every need, “Kalisi Mou” guarantees a truly exceptional charter experience.\n\nThe Lagoon 46 “Kalisi Mou” offers four spacious cabins and four toilets, ensuring privacy and convenience for all guests. Each cabin is meticulously designed with comfort in mind, providing a tranquil sanctuary where you can relax and unwind amidst the gentle rocking of the waves.\n\nWith an obligatory skipper at the helm, you can set sail with confidence and fully immerse yourself in the beauty of the sea. The skipper’s expertise and knowledge of the local waters will guide you to hidden gems and stunning destinations, ensuring a safe and memorable voyage.\n\nFor those seeking an elevated level of luxury and convenience, “Kalisi Mou” offers the option to have a hostess on board. The hostess will cater to your culinary desires, preparing delicious meals and refreshing beverages throughout your journey. Their presence adds a touch of indulgence, allowing you to fully savor the pleasures of your charter experience.\n\nThe Lagoon 46 “Kalisi Mou” is more than just a catamaran; it is a floating oasis that will captivate your senses and create lasting memories. From the moment you step on board, you will be greeted by elegance and sophistication. Whether you seek adventure, relaxation, or a perfect blend of both, “Kalisi Mou” is ready to exceed your expectations and offer you a charter experience like no other. So, sit back, embrace the sea breeze, and let “Kalisi Mou” transport you to a world of unparalleled beauty and serenity.","blueprint":{"name":"KA